\begin_layout Standard
In order to describe a single group where 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

contentious information" is being distributed, a special model is required to account for not only spreaders, but also counter spreaders of the information. The traditional ISR model serves as a good base for the new model, but has its shortcomings when examining the spread of contentious information. Examples of when to apply this ISCR model include populations where 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

